{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_5_level_main_05-02_beg","storyGroup":"main_5","storySort":3,"storyDependence":"main_5_level_main_05-01_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"5-2","storyName":"有口难言","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"诗怀雅并不如她表现的那样刻薄，但情况确实如她所说的糟糕。\n在一则机密通讯过后，陈决定请求罗德岛的协助。\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_05-02_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_05-02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":1,"next":3,"characters":["陈","星熊","诗怀雅","罗德岛干员","？？？"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第二关（后）","id":0},{"type":"Dialog","id":1},{"type":"Character","id":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"$newhope01_loop","volume":"0.6","crossfade":"1.5","delay":"0.5","id":4,"musicid":0},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_corridor","fadetime":"1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","name2":"char_010_chen_1#5","fadetime":"1","block":"true","focus":"2","id":7},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"诗怀雅，你没有这个权力。","id":9,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","id":10},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"唉。","id":11,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","name2":"char_010_chen_1#5","focus":"2","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"即使放下我们之间的私怨，我也不觉得你有这个能力来获得这份任命。","id":13,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你甚至可以口头声明——","id":14,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"“魏彦吾已向施警司发布命令，即刻起，施警司将接管近卫局一切事务，并罢免现行动组长，予以撤职处分”。","id":15,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你能吗？这条命令真的存在吗？","id":16,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","name2":"char_010_chen_1#5","focus":"1","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"嘁......别这么叫我。","id":18,"figure":"char_308_swire_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","name2":"char_010_chen_1#4","focus":"2","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"如果不能，就请你去完成自己的任务，现在接下这个烫手山芋对你没有好处，“诗小姐”。","id":20,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","name2":"char_010_chen_1#4","focus":"1","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"*龙门粗口*，说过多少次了，我不姓施！听好，我的代号是诗怀雅，或者叫我碧翠克斯·施怀雅警官，懂吗？","id":22,"figure":"char_308_swire_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","name2":"char_010_chen_1#4","focus":"2","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你那套规矩关我*龙门粗口*，你这代号和姓氏，普通人听了有谁知道区别。","id":24,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"哎。","id":26,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","name2":"char_010_chen_1#4","focus":"2","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"现在的我既没时间也没这个心情。请你让开点，自己去找点事做，乖。","id":28,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","name2":"char_010_chen_1#4","focus":"1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"姓陈的......你可真是*龙门粗口*。","id":30,"figure":"char_308_swire_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","name2":"char_010_chen_1#4","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"祝你*龙门粗口*富贵。","id":32,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","name2":"char_010_chen_1#4","focus":"1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"我走了，星熊。劝你管住这条疯龙，她死在哪里和我可是一点关系都没有。","id":34,"figure":"char_308_swire_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_308_swire_1#5","focus":"1","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"嗨，抱歉，“小姐”。你们的脾气其实都真够差的。不管她怎么说，刚才的援助还是谢谢你了。","id":36,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"下次不会了，我要看着她血流不止。","id":38,"figure":"char_308_swire_1#5"},{"type":"Dialog","id":39},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":40},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":41},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":42},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_dooropen","id":43},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":44},{"type":"Delay","id":45},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"她的背怎么了？像是新伤。","id":47,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"她夹着你冲进了掩体，整合运动术师的法术在她背后三米的墙上炸开了花。","id":49,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"偶尔也对她好点，没必要什么时候都互相针对成这个样子。","id":50,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......我知道。","id":52,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":53},{"type":"Character","id":54},{"type":"Text","text":"敲门声","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"我可以进来吗，龙门的陈长官？","id":56},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"进来吧。她不介意。不好意思，让你久等了。","id":58,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Dialog","id":59},{"type":"Character","id":60},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":61},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_012","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":62},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"没有的事，不用见外。","id":64,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"您好，陈长官。嗯......现在方便和罗德岛这边磋商一下任务内容吗？","id":65,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"我们已经集结了数支小队，他们正在甲板待命，准备好了随时和你们一同出发。","id":66,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"明白了，我马上就去。","id":68,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"抱歉听到了你和那位金发警官之间的对话......我们知道近卫局损失惨重。你可以相信我们，罗德岛能帮得上忙。","id":70,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......这不是我们现在该讨论的话题。","id":72,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":73},{"type":"Character","id":74},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":75},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":76},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"别介意，星熊。你也很清楚诗怀雅在做什么，她是在稳定局势。","id":78,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"她火气上头，你也是。","id":80,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我只是顺水推舟了一把。龙门损失惨重，这是“事实”，他们都应当知道的“事实”。","id":82,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"这不好，也不像是你会做的事。","id":84,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"这是为了龙门。","id":86,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"这么说话更不像你了，你是探长，是高级警司，不是政客，逢场作戏从来都不是你的天职。","id":88,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"这确实不是一个正规的警员该做的事，但我别无选择。","id":90,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":91},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"......","id":92,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"你太累了，需要好好放个假。","id":93,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"可能吧。","id":95,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"呵......我确实想过。","id":96,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"星熊，我需要一次很长很长的休假。","id":97,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":98},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"等这次的事情结束以后就去吧，别死撑着。","id":99,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"黄城，或者春都？要么就花郡吧，黄城离这里太远了，花在路上的时间够再休一次了。","id":100,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"还是回维多利亚见见校友？","id":101,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我想去你的家乡看看。","id":103,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"别去，没龙门有意思。","id":105,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"哈哈。","id":107,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":108},{"type":"stopmusic","id":109},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"3","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.6","id":111},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"嗯？","id":113,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"通讯。","id":115,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......是机密频道。","id":116,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"那我先出去。","id":118,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"麻烦你。","id":120,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":121},{"type":"Character","id":122},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":123},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.3","id":124},{"type":"Character","id":125},{"type":"Background","id":126},{"type":"Image","image":"bg_5_2_call","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","id":127},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"请说，我在听。","id":129},{"type":"Character","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"陈sir......那些感染者，整合运动......到处都是。","id":131},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"XR02？你在哪里？","id":133,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Character","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"木禾仓库。我中了几箭，应该活不长了。这是陷阱......","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"等他们都走了你再来这里。那个情报，我会留在身上。他们不会懂的。","id":136},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"代号XR02，你在那里等着。近卫局会立刻赶过去。你手上的情报有时效性，我们必须拿到手。","id":138,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Character","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我不确定，陈sir. 你有你的任务，我不想拖累你们。","id":140},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"XR02，不准死。你必须活下去。","id":142,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Character","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......我没法说服你，陈sir. 你们要小心。","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"等等，有动静。","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"【电流声】","id":146},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"XR02？XR02！","id":148,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......","id":149,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Dialog","id":150},{"type":"Character","id":151},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":152},{"type":"Image","id":153},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":154},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"星熊？","id":156,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"啊，在。","id":158,"figure":"char_136_hsguma"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"去整备队伍吧，我们该走了。","id":160,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","id":161},{"type":"Dialog","id":162},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.6","crossfade":"1.5","delay":"0.5","id":164,"musicid":1},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_uptown_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":165},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","fadetime":"1","focus":"2","id":167},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"陈长官，你要出发了吗？","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"罗德岛还剩下多少武装力量？","id":171,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"这不在可交换情报里，陈长官。我们接到的命令是辅助近卫局行动，但不能直接听从你的调遣，长官。","id":173,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":174},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我好像还没提出这种要求。","id":175,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"抱、抱歉，多言了。","id":177,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":178},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"没事。我只是想询问下罗德岛的状况，问问你们有没有安保上的难题，是否需要近卫局的帮助。","id":179,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"整合运动多次被击退，已经放弃进攻罗德岛本舰了。从种种迹象来看，龙门的形势要比罗德岛严峻得多。","id":181,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......","id":183,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"抱歉，这样形容好像不太对......","id":185,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"也就是说，你们并不需要近卫局的帮助。","id":187,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"是的。","id":189,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"那么暂时地，近卫局确实需要你们一点小小的帮助。","id":191,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"啊。","id":193,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"整合运动封锁了接泊区域的主干道。我需要打开一个缺口。近卫局的时间不多，请各位争分夺秒。","id":195,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"这是协议内容，长官，我们义不容辞。","id":197,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"那就好。跟我来！","id":199,"figure":"char_010_chen_1#1"},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.3","id":200},{"type":"Dialog","id":201},{"type":"Blocker","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"Image","id":203}],"characters":["陈","星熊","诗怀雅","罗德岛干员","？？？"]}